，論文三十餘篇。英國權威出版社 Routledge給予 &quot;中國和西方頂尖學者（leading Chinese and Western scholar）&quot; 的評價。<br />\n<br />\n《趙氏讀書生活》，一個歷史學者的視頻，分享學術、社會、政治經濟觀察<br />\n收費平台可獲參考資料和專欄分享，請以每月5元或更多的美元支持：<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/Chiusreading\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2FChiusreading&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0nwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=bf6ce248\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/Chiusreading</a><br />\n或於YOUTUBE 上按加入成為會員，可獲影片的參考資料<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCmi1...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCmi1...&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0nwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=d6a05ef9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCmi1...</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/drgavinchiu/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdrgavinchiu%2F&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0nwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=80ae258a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/drgavinchiu/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://PayPal.me/chiusreading\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FPayPal.me%2Fchiusreading&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0nwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=44192c07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">PayPal.me/chiusreading</a><br />\n工作洽談：higavinchiu@gmail.com<br />\n#國安法<br />\n#習近平新思代社會主義<br />\n#蕭若元<br />\nCaption author (Chinese (Taiwan))<br />\nKen Ko"},{"pid":"6e8d9ba2c9c044b81515686ba0310c28ff25555e","tid":2060581,"uid":262043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T13:53:57.000Z","msg":"點解咁少人睇"},{"pid":"a92b0b7003a11dc4fab568d6427bc1fd3ebc2aa6","tid":2060581,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e8d9ba2c9c044b81515686ba0310c28ff25555e","tid":2060581,"uid":262043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T13:53:57.000Z","msg":"點解咁少人睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T13:57:58.000Z","msg":"唔算少喎,  你自己睇下啲 vi